1. To build with the XLF compilers

./bld_ppc64le.sh

2. To run the conus experiment

cd ../rundir
bsub < conus.lsf

3. Data sources : 

Data from http://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/WG2bench/conus12km_data_v3
          http://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/WG2bench/conus_2.5_v3
http://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/WG2bench/conus12km_data_v3-2/conus12km_data_v3-2.tar.gz
http://www2.mmm.ucar.edu/wrf/src/WRFV3.8.1.TAR.gz

Copied to the downloads sub-directory for reference.


